{"tid":1806300,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：去年創自1884年最暖 平均氣溫達24.5度","createTime":"2020-01-01T08:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T08:49:14.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0be7246381e04fd6f341698c48ac015d644f4edc","tid":1806300,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】踏入2020年，天文台在facebook專頁表示，過去一年香港天氣異常溫暖，全年平均氣溫達到攝氏24.5度，是自1884年以來最暖的一年。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，去年平均氣溫比2015年的舊紀錄，還要高出0.3度。至於全年平均最高氣溫達到27.1度，平均最低氣溫也高達22.6度，同樣是有記錄以來最高。天文台呼籲，市民如不想無了冬天，記得要繼續節能減廢，愛惜地球。<br />\n<br />\n去年天文台總部氣溫達到12度或以下的的寒冷天氣日數只得1日，是有記錄以來最少寒冷日數的一年。不少網民留言認同，稱「今年（去年）真係暖咗好多」、「今年啲冬天衫冇得著呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%B5%E8%87%AA1884%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%9A%96-%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%BA%AB%E9%81%9424-5%E5%BA%A6-072000466.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%2587%25AA1884%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%259A%2596-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E9%2581%259424-5%25E5%25BA%25A6-072000466.html&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=90eb7478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%B5%E8%87%AA1884%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%9A%96-%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%BA%AB%E9%81%9424-5%E5%BA%A6-072000466.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c8ea81a7c5d5e101b9f895aaa4a765c5fbef6ec","tid":1806300,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"黐撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe324a191431d2e87318cf4c327147bf94b4071","tid":1806300,"uid":116350,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"藍屍會話<br />\n氣溫高？開大啲冷氣咪凍啲"},{"pid":"2290b81b7906e4ce89f26efb30dc7ed71f995b7d","tid":1806300,"uid":51569,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"藍屍：一日都係班暴徒成日燒雜物縱火又擲汽油彈，搞到熱哂"}]}